item.title: Srl antiradoms
item.dc:creator: @minitual minitual
item.description:
@minitual wrote:

FindNormalRandoms finds all of them. And the Sandwich lady doesn’t work unless you have a good computer with a fast video card. In the SRL/Core/Antirandoms.scar you can set UseSandwichLady=False if your computer isn’t solving it.
I noticed in some of your scripts you’re using indivisual random functions. Just delete those and add FindNormalRandoms, it handles all of them.
